	<h1 class="title">同时做400个项目，“就像时刻保持游泳状态的鱼”</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-04-29 13:41:30 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9020/medium/9020.jpg?1436688967" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


